    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as reliable daily transportation, though it shows its age in several areas. Mechanically, it starts and drives well, but you may notice some minor suspension noise over bumps and a slow oil drip that will eventually need attention. The exterior has several scratches and a small dent on the rear fender, while the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery and some fading on the dashboard. It is a solid, functional car for someone looking for budget-friendly transport who doesn't mind a few cosmetic and minor mechanical flaws.",
      "price": 19500.0,
