    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver that\u2019s ready to hit the road? This car is in honest, fair condition and is the perfect choice for someone who prioritizes mechanical reliability over a flawless exterior. It shows some typical cosmetic wear and tear from its time on the road, but it remains a sturdy, functional vehicle with plenty of life left to give!",
