    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a major project or a source for parts. The engine currently struggles with significant oil leaks and a rough idle, and the transmission has started to slip during gear shifts. Cosmetically, there is visible rust on the rocker panels, several deep dents on the passenger side, and the interior upholstery is heavily worn and torn. While it still starts, it will require substantial mechanical work and body repairs to be considered roadworthy again.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
